Review_Text: The delivery service was quite efficient, but I did encounter a small delay. Initially, I was given a delivery estimate of three days, but it took five days instead. The tracking system worked fine, but the updates were not as frequent as I would have liked. The package arrived in good condition, so that was a relief. If they can work on timeliness, it would be perfect.

I had high expectations, but my overall experience was disappointing. The website had issues, the delivery was late, and the product quality wasn’t up to the mark. On top of that, customer support was unhelpful when I raised my concerns. I don’t think I will be ordering from here again.

I placed an order and opted for express shipping, expecting to receive it within two days. However, it took over a week, and I received no proper updates. The tracking system was unreliable, and I had to contact customer support multiple times. They were polite but couldn't expedite the process. Eventually, the package arrived, but it was a frustrating experience. I hope they improve their logistics in the future.

The return process was smooth and hassle-free. I received a defective product and immediately contacted customer support. They arranged a return pickup within two days, and my refund was processed quickly. I appreciate the efficiency and customer-centric approach. I will shop here again, knowing they handle returns well.

Customer service kept giving generic responses and refused to take responsibility. It took almost a month to get my refund. This was my first and last time shopping here.
